{"tid":2342500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"學生擺街站促撤通識改革","createTime":"2020-12-27T07:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T10:51:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d75a66b376eceac915c5f5fc43098b9eaf36d8d","tid":2342500,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/VOLL7VJ3UBAKRAKR4QQEDTLLC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2FVOLL7VJ3UBAKRAKR4QQEDTLLC4%2F&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a1530025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201227%2FVOLL7VJ3UBAKRAKR4QQEDTLLC4%2F&h=418bd49f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201227/VOLL7VJ3UBAKRAKR4QQEDTLLC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n學生擺街站促撤通識改革<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eRFN7Mddwz3WcKp3lRt6I5bDjZ8=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5HVWK6NKJDIJEEX6IOYRS6WOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeRFN7Mddwz3WcKp3lRt6I5bDjZ8%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5HVWK6NKJDIJEEX6IOYRS6WOM.jpg&h=67960fde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「中學時政」成員被警員要求一字排開。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】教育局上月宣佈將向通識教育科「開刀」，包括將通識科改名、課時減半、學生須北上做專題研習、公開試只分及格與否等，更向仍設有初中通識科的學校施壓，勒令取消相關科目。有學生團體舉辦街站，堅決反對赤化教育改革，批評教育局順國安法殺科，只為令香港學生變成順民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警抄個人資料<br />\n<br />\n學生團體「中學時政」於荃灣擺街站，向途人派宣傳單張，反對教改打壓。團體並發起「全港撤回通識科改革聯署」，呼籲公眾掃描二維碼參加聯署。街站開始前，警員曾上前問在場傳媒「係咪影街站」，又記低在場網媒的個人資料。當團體成員到場後，警員隨即上前記低擺街站人士的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n「中學時政」發言人、就讀中四的Michael指出，現時教育局公佈的通識科教改中，有兩項特別受同學關注，包括送中研習及審查課本內容，「會唔會令學生因為睇唔到真實嘅歷史，從而對我哋嘅政權、社會有個錯誤嘅批判？」<br />\n<br />\nMichael說，今年通識教育科的課本內容已被大幅修改，以「今日香港」、「現代中國」課程改動尤為偏頗，「例如大躍進、文化大革命，大家都知道係共產黨黑歷史嘅鐵證，但係課本可能得返一版最後一句提一提」。<br />\n<br />\n他批評政府不應將現時民怨歸咎通識科，並將它變成洗腦工具，應正視人民憤怒的源頭。據他所知，現今校園氣氛惡劣，同學在課餘時間討論政治問題，都會被視為政治不正確，被老師訓斥。曾有一名同學因在Zoom上課時使用與抗爭相關的圖片作為頭像，被勒令停課一星期，「呢啲咁嘅政治打壓，喺香港咁耐以嚟其實都冇發生過」，他擔心校園中被白色恐怖籠罩，人人自危。"},{"pid":"16b5d9279d4be67bbfa9a0f09b1a475ad72413f8","tid":2342500,"uid":369075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85454c8aa13154e5835df153af086a5bb6d3da0b","tid":2342500,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a513a25f919290c3f201727a0a7f480c2d6b27c8","tid":2342500,"uid":276191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"勇敢的學生&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed14a2b396953cc68f3eccdb35f2bf6ea18ce2b6","tid":2342500,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a513a25f919290c3f201727a0a7f480c2d6b27c8","tid":2342500,"uid":276191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:47:56.000Z","msg":"勇敢的學生&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/